Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
calNegSlack(25.10)                                          calNegSlack(25.10)

Name
       calNegSlack

Syntax
       calNegSlack

       Reports  the  worst slack, total negative slack, and the number of vio-
       lating paths.

Example
       The calNegSlack command reports the total negative slack,  worst  nega-
       tive  slack,  and the number of violating paths. You can also find this
       report in the log file.

       calNegSlack

       Total negative slacks(TNS)= xxx

       Worst negative slacks(WNS)= xxx

       Number of violating paths= xxx

